          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Risk-Based Credit Examination Act</b></p> <p>This bill provides the Securities and Exchange Commission's Office of Credit Ratings with discretion concerning reviewable matters during its annual examination of nationally recognized statistical rating organizations.</p>]]>
